-- TIGHT FORMS: prefix, tight infix, juxtaposition

-- Prefix forms
=== prefix negative | 80
-x

=== prefix colon | 80
:foo

=== prefix tilde | 80
~[1 2 3]

-- Tight infix forms
=== dot notation | 80
x.y

=== dot chain | 80
a.b.c.d

=== tight colon | 80
foo:bar

-- Juxtaposition
=== function call | 80
f(x)

=== chained calls | 80
f(x)(y)

=== indexing | 80
f(x)[i]

=== complex juxt | 80
foo(bar)[baz](qux)

-- PAGE in tight context
=== juxt with page | 80
x.b'''
   page content
   '''

=== juxt with multiline page | 80
foo'''
   line one
   line two
   '''

=== dot chain with page | 80
a.b.c'''
     multi
     line
     '''

-- SPAN in tight context
=== juxt with span | 80
x.'''span content'''

=== juxt with multiline span | 80
foo.'''line one
       line two'''

=== dot chain with span | 80
a.b.c.'''hello'''

=== function call with span arg | 80
f('''arg with "quotes"''')
